#: ../../modisTab.rst:274
msgid "MODIS conversion"
msgstr ""

#: ../../modisTab.rst:276
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select file MODIS` |open_file|: select a MODIS image (file "
".hdf);"
msgstr ""

#: ../../modisTab.rst:277
msgid ""
"|checkbox| :guilabel:`Reproject to WGS 84`: if checked, reproject bands "
"to WGS 84, required for use in :guilabel:`SCP`;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../modisTab.rst:278
msgid ""
"|checkbox| :guilabel:`Use value as  NoData` |input_number|: if checked, "
"pixels having ``NoData`` value are not counted during conversion and the "
"DOS1 calculation of DNmin; it is useful when image has a black border "
"(usually pixel value = -999);"
msgstr ""

#: ../../modisTab.rst:279
msgid ""
"|checkbox| :guilabel:`Create Band set and use Band set tools`: if "
"checked, bands are added to the active :guilabel:`Band set` after the "
"conversion; also, the :guilabel:`Band set` is processed according to the "
"tools checked in the :ref:`band_set_tab`;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../modisTab.rst:280
msgid ""
"|checkbox| :guilabel:`Add bands in a new Band set`: if checked, bands are"
" added to a new empty :guilabel:`Band set` after the conversion;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../modisTab.rst:285
msgid "Metadata"
msgstr ""

#: ../../modisTab.rst:287
msgid ""
"All the bands found in the :guilabel:`Select file MODIS` are listed in "
"the table :guilabel:`Metadata`. For information about "
":guilabel:`Metadata` fields visit `the MODIS page "
"<https://lpdaac.usgs.gov/dataset_discovery/modis>`_ ."
msgstr ""

